::DrillBit::

He heard all the comm chatter in the command center. He opened a comm.
"Dollen, I want you with me. Get up here now."
He opened a link to DarkFate.
"I've been a little out of the loop, whats going on?"

::Dollen::

He headed to the command center, and stood next to DrillBit.

::Epyon::

He opened a comm to Prowl.
"When do you want to get this plan of ours started?"

::Hot Rod::

He went to his room, and tryed to relax a little.
